2025-12-05IRCC, GAC, TBFinancial Administration ActCertain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Morocco Earthquake) Remission OrderCertain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Morocco Earthquake) Remission Order in order to remit fees associated with travel documents, citizenship certificates and consular services that were not collected for Canadians and permanent residents of Canada affected by the earthquakes occurring in Morocco on September 8, 2023.N/A
subject: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Morocco Earthquake) Remission Order
precis: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Morocco Earthquake) Remission Order in order to remit fees associated with travel documents, citizenship certificates and consular services that were not collected for Canadians and permanent residents of Canada affected by the earthquakes occurring in Morocco on September 8, 2023.
